        <cdata>
          <text>&lt;p&gt;This bill prohibits the Department of Defense from requiring individuals to wear masks on military installations inside the United States for the purpose of preventing the spread of COVID-19.&lt;/p&gt;</text>
        </cdata>
      </summary>
